<h3>Hiding Options In Product Details</h3><p>This is used if you want to enable the built in form field validation scripts, but want to have more control over how your options appear in your catalog.&nbsp; </p><p>If you want to copy and paste your option HTML code into the details section of a product and also want the built in form field validation then place a checkmark next to the options to include with this product and then place a checkmark in this box.&nbsp; When the details of the product are displayed for the customer no option form fields will be shown above the details area.</p>




